Evaluations.Expression: smChannelHasExcessiveNoise = smTestForExcessiveNoisePreset AND ((smChannelHasExcessiveNoiseAboveAnalysisThreshold AND smTestExcessiveNoiseAboveOrBelowAnalysisThreshold) OR (smChannelHasExcessiveNoiseAboveDetectionThreshold AND NOT smTestExcessiveNoiseAboveOrBelowAnalysisThreshold))
smInferredFFLeft = smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft AND smHeightBelowFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter
smInferredFFRight = smPartOfExtendedLocusRight AND smHeightBelowFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter
smInferredPullupFFLeft = smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft AND smHeightBelowPullupFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisablePullupFractionalFilter
smInferredPullupFFRight = smPartOfExtendedLocusRight AND smHeightBelowPullupFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisablePullupFractionalFilter

smFFLeft = ((smBelowFractionalFilterLeft AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter) OR (smBelowPullupFractionalFilterLeft AND NOT smDisablePullupFractionalFilter) OR smInferredFFLeft OR smInferredPullupFFLeft)

smFFRight = ((smBelowFractionalFilterRight AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter) OR (smBelowPullupFractionalFilterRight AND NOT smDisablePullupFractionalFilter) OR smInferredFFRight OR smInferredPullupFFRight)
smExtendedFractionalFilter = ((NOT smPartOfExtendedLocusRight AND smFFLeft) OR (NOT smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft AND smFFRight) OR (smFFLeft AND smFFRight)) AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter

smUnassignedInterlocusPeak = NOT (smPeakInCoreLadderLocus OR smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft OR smPartOfExtendedLocusRight OR smSampleIsLadder OR smSignalIsCtrlPeak OR smUnexpectedILSPeak OR smChannelIsILS)
smPurePullup = smPullUp AND NOT smPrimaryInterchannelLink AND NOT smNotInterchannelLink
smTemp3Left = sm1UnambiguousPeakLeft AND NOT smSignalOffGridLeft AND smTemp1Left
smTemp6Left = sm0UnambiguousPeaksLeft AND sm1AmbiguousPeakLeft AND sm1UnambiguousPeakRight
smTemp7Left = sm0UnambiguousPeaksLeft AND sm2PlusAmbiguousPeaksRight AND NOT smSignalOffGridLeft AND smTemp1Left
smTemp9Left = sm2PlusUnambiguousPeaksLeft AND sm2PlusUnambiguousPeaksRight AND smSignalOffGridRight AND NOT smPurePullup AND NOT smSignalOffGridLeft
smTemp3Right = sm1UnambiguousPeakRight AND NOT smSignalOffGridRight AND smTemp1Right
smTemp6Right = sm0UnambiguousPeaksRight AND sm1AmbiguousPeakRight AND sm1UnambiguousPeakLeft
smTemp7Right = sm0UnambiguousPeaksRight AND sm2PlusAmbiguousPeaksLeft AND NOT smSignalOffGridRight AND smTemp1Right
smTemp9Right = sm2PlusUnambiguousPeaksRight AND sm2PlusUnambiguousPeaksLeft AND smSignalOffGridLeft AND NOT smPurePullup AND NOT smSignalOffGridRight
smCouldBelongToLocusLeft = (smTemp2Left OR smTemp3Left OR smTemp5Left OR smTemp6Left OR smTemp7Left OR smTemp9Left) AND NOT smPeakInCoreLadderLocus
smCouldBelongToLocusRight = (smTemp2Right OR smTemp3Right OR smTemp5Right OR smTemp6Right OR smTemp7Right OR smTemp9Right) AND NOT smPeakInCoreLadderLocus
smInterlocusPullUp = (NOT (smPeakInCoreLadderLocus OR smSampleIsLadder OR smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft OR smPartOfExtendedLocusRight OR smSignalIsCtrlPeak OR smChannelIsILS)) AND smPurePullup
smInterlocusPullUpWithPoorFit = smInterlocusPullUp AND (smPoorPeakMorphology OR smCurveFitMarginal OR smCurveFitFailed)
smPullupAtExtraneousILSPeak = smChannelIsILS AND smPurePullup AND smUnexpectedILSPeak
smPossibleValidInterlocusLeft = smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft AND NOT (smFFLeft OR smInterlocusPullUp)
smPossibleValidInterlocusRight = smPartOfExtendedLocusRight AND NOT (smFFRight OR smInterlocusPullUp)

Triggers.TriggerExpression: smStutter (NOT smBelowMinRFU AND NOT smDisableStutterFilter): smNumberOfStuttersInSample
smAdenylation (NOT smBelowMinRFU AND NOT smDisableAdenylationFilter): smNumberOfAdenylationsInSample

smUnexpectedPeakInNegativeControl ((NOT smPeakToRightOfILS) AND (NOT smBelowMinRFU OR (smBelowMinRFU AND smTestForPeaksBelowMinRFUForNegCtrlPreset))): smUnexpectedNoOfPeaks, smUnexpectedNoOfPeaksInChannel, smNegCtrlFailed
smLaserOffScalePrimary (NOT smCraterSidePeak AND NOT smSignalNotACraterSidePeak): smLocusHasPeaksWithLaserSaturation, smSomePeaksHaveLaserOffScale
smLaserOffScaleNoInterchannelLink (NOT smCraterSidePeak AND NOT smSignalNotACraterSidePeak): smLocusHasPeaksWithLaserSaturation, smSomePeaksHaveLaserOffScale

Evaluations.Expression: smRestrictedPriorityPeak = (smHeightBelowInterlocusMinRFU OR smBelowMinRFU OR (smStutter AND NOT smDisableStutterFilter) OR ((smAdenylation AND NOT smDisableAdenylationFilter) AND NOT (smCallOnLadderAdenylationPreset AND NOT smSignalOL)) OR (smHeightBelowFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter) OR (smHeightBelowPullupFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisablePullupFractionalFilter) OR smInterlocusPullUp OR (smExtendedFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter) OR smPullupAtExtraneousILSPeak) AND NOT (smSampleIsNegCtrl OR smSignalIsCtrlPeak)
smSignalIsPullupAndPoorMorphologyOrResidualInMultiAllele = smPurePullup AND smPreliminaryLocusHas2OrMoreAlleles AND smBPResidualTooLarge AND NOT smRestrictedPriorityPeak
smPullUpAtAllele = smSignalIsAllele AND smPurePullup AND NOT smPeakIsNotAnAllele AND NOT smRestrictedPriorityPeak
smAlleleHasExcessiveResidual = smBPResidualTooLarge AND smSignalIsAllele AND NOT smSignalIsPullupAndPoorMorphologyOrResidualInMultiAllele
smAlleleOL = smSignalOL AND smSignalIsAllele AND NOT smPeakIsNotAnAllele AND NOT smRestrictedPriorityPeak
smActuallyAnAllele = smSignalIsAllele AND NOT smPeakIsNotAnAllele AND NOT smRestrictedPriorityPeak AND NOT smSampleIsLadder AND NOT smChannelIsILS AND NOT smUnassignedInterlocusPeak
smCoreAlleleIsOL = smActuallyAnAllele AND smAlleleOL AND smPeakInCoreLadderLocus

smNotAKnownArtifact = NOT ((smStutter AND NOT smDisableStutterFilter) OR (smAdenylation AND NOT smDisableAdenylationFilter) OR (smPullUp AND NOT smNotInterchannelLink) OR smSpike OR (((smHeightBelowFractionalFilter OR smExtendedFractionalFilter)) AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter AND smIncludeFractionalFilterAmongKnownArtifactsToEvaluateSubAnalyticPeaksPreset))

Triggers.TriggerExpression: smPurePullupLateStage (NOT smRestrictedPriorityPeak AND NOT (smSampleIsNegCtrl OR smSignalIsCtrlPeak)): smNumberOfPullUpsInSample
smLocusContainsCrater (NOT smSampleIsLadder AND NOT smSampleIsNegCtrl): smLocusSummaryNumberOfCraters

Evaluations.Expression: smLocusUnderAmped = ((smLocusHasPeaksBetweenDetectionAndAnalysisThresholds AND (smNoGenotypeFound OR smHomozygoteHeightProblem OR (smLocusHasPeaksBelowMinRFUThatAreNotKnownArtifacts AND smLocusIsHomozygous))) OR (smAmpMoreOnLowHomozygotePreset AND (smNoGenotypeFound OR smHomozygoteHeightProblem))) AND NOT smSampleIsNegCtrl AND NOT smNoYLinkedAlleleExpected

Triggers.TriggerExpression: smLocusIsHomozygous (NOT smSampleIsNegCtrl AND NOT smLocusIsYLinked): smTotalNumberOfHomozygousLoci
